  "title": "Equipment Automation Engineer (MNC / East)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure all machines are in good working condition to support smooth production with zero defects.</li>\n  <li>Perform immediate on-site troubleshooting in the event of any machine issues.</li>\n  <li>Escalate and coordinate with suppliers for unresolved issues, providing remote support as required.</li>\n  <li>Set up and verify process flow to ensure efficient and stable operations.</li>\n  <li>Monitor machine performance to meet targeted UPH and cycle time.</li>\n  <li>Provide NPI support for automation systems to ensure smooth implementation and issue-free startup.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
